				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p169552">Re: Help with sound emulation</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=169552#p169552"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Wed Apr 27, 2016 8:28 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
